h3 id=\"启用LTPA认证\"><a href=\"#启用LTPA认证\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启用LTPA认证\"></a>启用LTPA认证</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602105304578.png\" alt=\"image-20230602105304578\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"限制主机访问更改控制台端口\"><a href=\"#限制主机访问更改控制台端口\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"限制主机访问更改控制台端口\"></a>限制主机访问更改控制台端口</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602105354676.png\" alt=\"image-20230602105354676\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"启用安全审计\"><a href=\"#启用安全审计\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"启用安全审计\"></a>启用安全审计</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602105914408.png\" alt=\"image-20230602105914408\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"单点登陆，防止xss\"><a href=\"#单点登陆，防止xss\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"单点登陆，防止xss\"></a>单点登陆，防止xss</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602105926863.png\" alt=\"image-20230602105926863\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602110052784.png\" alt=\"image-20230602110052784\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"防止通过浏览器查看目录\"><a href=\"#防止通过浏览器查看目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"防止通过浏览器查看目录\"></a>防止通过浏览器查看目录</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602110137994.png\" alt=\"image-20230602110137994\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"限制config和properties目录权限\"><a href=\"#限制config和properties目录权限\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"限制config和properties目录权限\"></a>限制config和properties目录权限</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602110611257.png\" alt=\"image-20230602110611257\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"jenkins安全加固\"><a href=\"#jenkins安全加固\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"jenkins安全加固\"></a>jenkins安全加固</h2><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602133417776.png\" alt=\"image-20230602133417776\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602133538642.png\" alt=\"image-20230602133538642\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602133936983.png\" alt=\"image-20230602133936983\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"为多用户分配权限\"><a href=\"#为多用户分配权限\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"为多用户分配权限\"></a>为多用户分配权限</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602140604207.png\" alt=\"image-20230602140604207\"></p>\n<p>关闭跨站请求伪造保护</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">[root@node1 ~]# vim &#x2F;usr&#x2F;lib&#x2F;systemd&#x2F;system&#x2F;jenkins.service \nEnvironment&#x3D;&quot;JAVA_OPTS&#x3D;-Djava.awt.headless&#x3D;true -Dhudson.security.csrf.GlobalCrumbIssuerConfiguration.DISABLE_CSRF_PROTECTION&#x3D;true&quot;\n[root@node1 ~]# systemctl daemon-reload \n[root@node1 ~]# systemctl restart jenkins\n之后再次查看此位置就会发现有\n“跨站请求伪造保护\nThis configuration is unavailable because the System property hudson.security.csrf.GlobalCrumbIssuerConfiguration.DISABLE_CSRF_PROTECTION is set to true.That option should be considered unsupported and its use should be limited to working around compatibility problems until they are resolved.”\n字样的内容提示。</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"修改默认端口-1\"><a href=\"#修改默认端口-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改默认端口\"></a>修改默认端口</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-photobank.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img_for_typora/image-20230602144534997.png\" alt=\"image-20230602144534997\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"IIS安全加固\"><a href=\"#IIS安全加固\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"IIS安全加固\"></a>IIS安全加固</h2><p>环境：Windows server 2008</p>\n<p>安装IIS（除了 IIS6 管理兼容性 其他都勾选）</p>\n<h3 id=\"建立测试站点\"><a href=\"#建立测试站点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建立测试站点\"></a>建立测试站点</h3><p><img src=\"https://abyssaler-typora-ph